<span style="color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">大数据电子商务有限公司</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">将按照较低的定价向用户销售该商品；</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0;font-size:14px">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">6.1.1.2 </span>
<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">如果某一商品的正确定价高于错误定价，</span></span>
<span style="color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">大数据电子商务有限公司</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0;font-size:14px">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">将根据具体情况，在交付前联系用户寻求指示</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;">, </span>
