<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0;font-size:14px">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">6.3 </span>
<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">服务通知</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0;font-size:14px">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">6.3.1 </span>
