<span style="color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">任性购商城</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">公布内容为准。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
