<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">服务表示用户同意接受修订的后的协议或规则。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;"><br></span></p><h2 style="text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:18px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:20px 0 0;">
