<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">7.3 </span>
<span style="color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">大数据电子商务有限公司</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">不担保</span>
<span style="color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">任性购商城</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">提供给用户的全部信息，从</span>
<span style="color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">任性购商城</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">或其服务器发出的电子邮件、信息等没有病毒或其他有害成份。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
