<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0;font-size:14px">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">7.4 </span>
<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">如因不可抗力或其他</span></span>
