<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0;font-size:14px">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">8.2 </span>
<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">下列情形，</span></span>
<span style="color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">大数据电子商务有限公司</span>
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">可以通过注销用户的方式终止服务：</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:#FFFFFF;margin:0;">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0;font-size:14px">
<span style="font-family:Arial;color:#707070;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;">8.2.1 </span>
<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">用户违反本协议相关规定，</span></span>
